Placeholder so the firmware/ directory exists on every checkout.

builtins.path in flake-modules/hosts/ali-mba-linux/default.nix reads this
directory at eval time; it must exist on disk. The actual firmware files
(all_firmware.tar.gz, kernelcache*) are non-redistributable Apple peripheral
firmware, gitignored, and must be copied from /boot/asahi/ on the MBA itself
before the first `nixos-rebuild`.

See /tmp/ali-mba-linux-bringup.md (or the host's hardware-configuration.nix
comments) for the copy step.
